aweme_list.desc: If Batman had a timepiece, it would be as elaborate and advanced and stunning as Gotham City...in its black version.  Jacob Arabo, the founder, chairman, and creatice director of Jacob and Co. is behind the design process for this unique piece.  A mirror-polished rose gold case like this one is befitting of someone like Bruce Wayne. The Gotham City is destined for a Jacob & Co. audience that also relates to his secret identity : that of a playboy billionaire, nonchalant and gifted with extremely good taste. The duality of the comic's character invented by Bob Kane is furthered in the Gotham City. The 18K Rose gold version of the Gotham City is edited as a 36-piece limited series. #jacobandco #inspiredbytheimpossible #gothamcity #brucewayne

original_client_text.markup_text:
If Batman had a timepiece, it would be as elaborate and advanced and stunning as Gotham City...in its black version.

Jacob Arabo, the founder, chairman, and creatice director of Jacob and Co. is behind the design process for this unique piece. A mirror-polished rose gold case like this one is befitting of someone like Bruce Wayne.

The Gotham City is destined for a Jacob & Co. audience that also relates to his secret identity : that of a playboy billionaire, nonchalant and gifted with extremely good taste. The duality of the comic's character invented by Bob Kane is furthered in the Gotham City. The 18K Rose gold version of the Gotham City is edited as a 36-piece limited series.

#jacobandco #inspiredbytheimpossible #gothamcity #brucewayne
